text: An artistic representation of a lively green frog wearing a pair of colorful swimming goggles. The frog is amusingly placed in a typical human situation. It is trying to catch a bus in a bustling city, standing next to a sign that reads 'bus stop'. There are tall buildings in the background, lights from car headlights, and a group of diverse people, including a black man and a white woman, waiting along with the frog. It is evening and the city is bathed in the gentle, warm light of the setting sun.
